{
  "texts": [
    "First, although we rigorously broadened the databases and search terms, it was still probable that some research was omitted.",
    "Second, as the extent is limited to English material published within the past decade, we might have missed prior research to this time (or conducted in a different language).",
    "Third, the undertaken quality assessment could have screened out valuable articles providing differing findings.",
    "Fourth, we were unable to conduct a quantitative analysis of the evidence as it fell outside this SLR scope due to the heterogeneity in our selection study.",
    "We also could not thoroughly analyze the bias risks or integrity of the reported articles due to related gaps."
  ]
}